description.narrative: Protection of Human Dignity in Humanitarian Crisis

Working with other Essential Package of Health Services (EPHS) implementers, Trocaire aims to strengthen Somali ownership and sustainability of the health sector and increase use and access to reproductive, nutrition, child and maternal health services as delivered by the EPHS. This will ultimately improve the health of Somalis which leads to improved human development and economic development outcomes for Somalia.
